<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Add your CSS here or use the external style.css file */
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="logo">Smart-Farm<span>Solutions</span></h1>
            <p class="tagline">Empowering local farmers with smart technology</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="section" id="goal">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Define Your Goal</h2>
            <p>Our goal is to provide smart technology solutions that empower local farmers to achieve sustainability and efficiency in their farming practices.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="audience">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Understand Your Audience</h2>
            <p>We understand the unique challenges faced by local farmers and offer tailored solutions that address their specific needs and help them overcome their pain points.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="headline">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Craft a Compelling Headline</h2>
            <p>Transform Your Farm with Data-Driven Smart Technology Solutions</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="content">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Create Engaging Content</h2>
            <p>Discover how our innovative technology can increase your farm's productivity and sustainability. Learn from the success stories of farmers who have already benefited from our solutions.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="design">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Design for Usability</h2>
            <p>Our platform is designed with simplicity in mind. Enjoy a seamless user experience with intuitive navigation on any device.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Optimize Your Call-To-Action</h2>
            <p>Take the first step towards transforming your farming practices. Start your journey with our smart farming solutions today!</p>
            <button class="cta-button" onclick="showPopup()">Get Started Now</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="form">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Include a Form</h2>
            <p>Sign up now for a personalized consultation to see how our technology can benefit your farm.</p>
            <form id="consultationForm">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                <button type="submit">Get Consultation</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Smart-Farm Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Popup Modal -->
    <div class="popup-modal" id="popupModal">
        <div class="popup-content">
            <span class="close-btn" onclick="closePopup()">&times;</span>
            <h3>Welcome to Smart-Farm Solutions</h3>
            <p>Thank you for your interest! We will contact you shortly to discuss how our smart farming solutions can benefit your agricultural practices.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showPopup() {
            document.getElementById('popupModal').style.display = 'block';
        }

        function closePopup() {
            document.getElementById('popupModal').style.display = 'none';
        }

        document.getElementById('consultationForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
            event.preventDefault();

            const name = document.querySelector('input[name="name"]').value;
            const email = document.querySelector('input[name="email"]').value;

            if (name && email) {
                showPopup();

                fetch('/api/submit-form', {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: {
                        'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                    },
                    body: JSON.stringify({ name, email })
                })
                .then(response => response.json())
                .then(data => {
                    console.log('Success:', data);
                    alert('Form submitted successfully!');
                })
                .catch((error) => {
                    console.error('Error:', error);
                    alert('There was an error submitting the form.');
                });
            } else {
                alert('Please fill out all fields.');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
